name: Awake (itch) (Keltfire)
description:
Awaken to a mysterious, surreal landscape, and see if you can make it to the end!

This game is made for the Game Dev Knockout (GDKO) 2023 Round 1!

Skybox made by Avionx: https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/2d/textures-materials/sky/skybox-series-free-103633

Text font is Bubble Font by JazzCreate: https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/2d/fonts/bubble-font-free-version-24987

All sound effects from mixkit: https://mixkit.co/free-sound-effects/

All scripts and other assets are made by me!
